name: Dystopia | Provocateur
description:
In a world that is about to suffer total destruction, the 'security forces' are not tasked with protecting the public, but tasked with protecting and maintaining existing authorities.  

They oppress the poor, evict people from their own homes under the pretext of "public assets" and "for the sake of national security".  But what they actually doing is solely for the benefit of the ruler, the interests of the privileged people of this world that will soon be destroyed.  

They don't care, 
They let us die.
